Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.34,0:00:19.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸は慣れない音のために手傷を負い
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.77,0:00:22.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ミオという少女の世話になる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.14,0:00:28.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ミオは、戦で行き場をなくした子供たちと暮らしを立てていた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.48,0:00:33.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だが、百鬼丸が鬼神との戦いに出かけたその夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.37,0:00:40.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんなの…あんなのってねぇよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:42.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ん？なんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.21,0:00:49.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ…あにき！あにき！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.67,0:00:50.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうしたんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.80,0:00:53.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,坊やかい？ちょうどよかった 手を貸しておく…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.26,0:00:54.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき！大丈夫か！？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.68,0:00:58.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきの足が！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.30,0:01:03.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やっぱり手負いじゃ無理があったのさ  鬼神に取られちまった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.27,0:01:08.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき！痛ぇのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.40,0:01:09.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,…え？今の声…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.23,0:01:13.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あぁ  足は取られたが声は取り戻したらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.57,0:01:18.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきの…声…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.08,0:01:24.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,Party is over
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.96,0:01:29.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それでも踊りたかった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.59,0:01:35.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,眠れないくらい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.13,0:01:42.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,情熱の火はいつしか　いつの日にか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.89,0:01:45.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はなから気付いている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.81,0:01:48.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,炎はいつか消える
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.52,0:01:51.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何も要らないはずだった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.36,0:01:54.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なのにまだ I'm so serious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.86,0:02:00.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ああ　まだ間に合う
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.49,0:02:05.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ああ ただ Burn it up Baby
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.54,0:02:08.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,Sorry darling そんなに甘くないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.50,0:02:11.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でもきっとそんなに悪くないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.88,0:02:14.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ああ Give me fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.84,0:02:17.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,Light it up Baby 燃やしちゃうぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.57,0:02:37.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,Party is over
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.32,0:02:39.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,Sorry darling Hurry up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.16,0:02:42.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ああただBurn it up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.99,0:02:45.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,Give me fire
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.87,0:02:49.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,Light it up Baby 燃やしちゃうぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.12,0:02:53.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,#6 The story of the Moriko Song, part 2
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.43,0:03:01.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ミオ姉！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.84,0:03:02.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おかえり！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.97,0:03:04.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ただいま！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.39,0:03:07.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.56,0:03:11.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうしたんだよ！ケガしてるじゃねぇか！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:16.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大したことないよ ちょっと転んじゃって…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.48,0:03:19.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大丈夫か？早く休まねぇと…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.74,0:03:23.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やっぱり両方の陣で働くなんて無理なんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:24.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今までどおり…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:25.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それは!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.91,0:03:28.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あぁ…それがさぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.33,0:03:34.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.71,0:03:37.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何があったの？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:40.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,命にゃ別状ないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.38,0:03:43.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ま、戦うには早すぎたのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:49.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ミオ姉…人のことはいいから早く寝ろって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.81,0:03:53.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でも…私のほうが慣れてるから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:56.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんたはみんなの食事をね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:16.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,くそっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:22.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうしたんだよ急に！兄貴のそばについてなくていいのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.26,0:04:24.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.30,0:04:26.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まぁ、ミオ姉がいれば安心だけどな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.18,0:04:33.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まったく…ミオ姉の世話好きにも困ったもんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:36.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ひと晩じゅう働いて疲れてるってのに…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:41.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,タケ  お前姉ちゃんが働いてるとこ見たことあるのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.40,0:04:43.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,俺はいつも留守番だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.45,0:04:45.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,チビたちだけ残しとけねぇからな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.78,0:04:46.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうか…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.99,0:04:52.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,しょうがねぇよ！今はミオ姉の稼ぎがなきゃみんな餓死するしかねぇんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:54.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,別に責めちゃいねぇよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:59.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,俺たちさ、約束してんだよ  俺たちの田んぼを持つって
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.92,0:05:00.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,田んぼ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.17,0:05:07.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あぁ  夏は一面、ダーッと青くて 秋には黄金色になる田んぼだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.51,0:05:08.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,黄金色だぞ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.89,0:05:11.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それで米が食いきれねぇほど取れるんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.52,0:05:18.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,俺たちは戦で丸焼けか 日照りでカラカラの田んぼしか見たことねぇけど
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.52,0:05:21.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ミオ姉が子供の頃はそうだったって
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:26.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いつか…私たちの田んぼを持とうね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.11,0:05:31.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,青くて黄金色で、私たちだけの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.79,0:05:38.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もう少しすりゃあ、俺も働きに行けるし そしたらミオ姉に楽させてやるよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.33,0:05:40.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おーい！タケちゃーん！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:42.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あぁ！今行く！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.22,0:05:47.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大丈夫！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.47,0:05:50.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戦でたくさんなくしたぶん、戦から取り戻すだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:05:59.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ここらでひと雨来てもらわにゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.27,0:06:04.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まぁ、毎年必ず恵みの雨はあるからなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.32,0:06:07.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ、ホレ  少し雲が出てきとるが…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.41,0:06:11.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お願いです、父上！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:14.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私を酒井討伐の援軍にお加えください！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:18.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あのような小国、すぐに攻め落としてみせましょう！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:23.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戦を侮るな！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:28.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そのような気構えでは、まだまだ初陣は早い！鍛錬に励め
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:29.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,父上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.12,0:06:29.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,多宝丸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:32.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,母上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:39.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,母上 私を戦に出していただけるよう 母上からも父上にお口添えください！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:42.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,父上がならぬとおっしゃったのでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.31,0:06:44.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ならばわたくしが言おうと同じことです
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:47.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,父上はわかっておられぬのです！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.32,0:06:49.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,出陣さえお許しいただければ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.57,0:06:53.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,きっと母上にお喜びいただけるような武勲を上げてみせます！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.37,0:06:55.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,武勲など…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:58.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私の武勲などいりませぬか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:07:00.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうではありませぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:03.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いえ…母上はいつもそうです
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:07.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,狩りでどれほどの獲物を仕留めようと 武術の腕を上げようと
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.55,0:07:09.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,母上はお喜びにならない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.72,0:07:11.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わたくしはただ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:15.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戦にまつわるものを好まぬのです
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:18.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,好まぬのは戦ではなく、私でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:20.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何をそのような！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:24.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,多宝丸！わが子を厭う母がどこにおりましょうや
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.24,0:07:37.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,兵庫！陸奥！早駆けじゃ 馬を引け！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.04,0:07:37.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はっ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:43.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,若！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:47.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,言いたいことはわかっておる！少し子供じみていたな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:48.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,少し？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.26,0:07:55.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,御方様はお優しい  若にはいつも…いつも
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:57.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,一度言えばわかる！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.60,0:08:04.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,母上が私に冷たかったことなどない…しかし…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.31,0:08:08.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,若、若！危のうございます！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:10.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ケガをされては！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.49,0:08:12.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,兵庫、陸奥！若を！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.53,0:08:16.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,母上！見てください母上！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.66,0:08:20.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,若！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.12,0:08:23.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,若！何をされているのです
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:25.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,聞こえているのですか！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:30.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,母上には、何よりも強く想いを寄せるものがある
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:35.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,決して口には出されぬが…何かを隠しておられる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.18,0:08:39.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いや…母上だけではない  父上も
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.01,0:08:44.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わたくしどもは、国ごと小さな礎ひとつの上に乗っていることを
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.15,0:08:46.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お忘れなきようにと
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.07,0:08:55.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,一体…お2人には何が
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:22.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.06,0:09:25.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まだ寝てなきゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.44,0:09:34.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,行ったらダメよ 悔しいのはわかるけど 無茶をして死んでしまったら元も子もない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.36,0:09:39.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私もね、少し焦って無理しちゃって
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:41.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,バカだね…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.20,0:09:44.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,稼ぐのは簡単じゃないってわかってたのに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.87,0:09:49.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ダメダメ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:54.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,二度と侍なんかのために泣かないって決めたんだから 泣いたら負け
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.17,0:09:57.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸もね 無理して死んじゃったら負けよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:10:01.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,れより、声が出るようになったんでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.26,0:10:03.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,すごいじゃない！ちょっと喋ってみて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:08.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うるさいってこと？自分の声が？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.11,0:10:12.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:17.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,すぐに慣れるわよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.82,0:10:22.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どろろが言ってたよ？今のままじゃ 穴ぐらにこもった獣みたいだって
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:28.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうだ！歌は？百鬼丸好きでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.08,0:10:33.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,赤い花つんで
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.71,0:10:37.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私ね、泣きそうになったら歌うの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.09,0:10:39.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,泣く代わりに ね？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:47.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,赤い花つんで
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.93,0:10:52.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの人にあげよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:58.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの人の髪に
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.11,0:11:03.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この花さ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.20,0:11:04.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,行くのかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.66,0:11:08.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あぁ　あの姉さんの言うとおり 、焦らず行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.37,0:11:14.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,鬼神のいる道を迂回すりゃいいことさ どうせ急ぐ旅じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.09,0:11:19.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ただ、いくら百鬼丸にそれを説いたって無駄だろうねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.42,0:11:20.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:24.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,赤ん坊がおもちゃを取られたら怒って取り戻すだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.76,0:11:26.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それと同じなのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.56,0:11:30.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そのうえ、取られたモンが自分の身体とあっちゃねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:34.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの歌を聞いてるときは静まるようだが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.81,0:11:36.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,静まるって？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:41.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸が赤ん坊のときから持ってる鬼神の炎さ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:48.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,身体を奪われたときの残り火… みたいなモンかもしれないがね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:54.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,穴ぐらから出てきたモンが 鬼だったってことがならねぇようにしなよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.92,0:11:56.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,じゃあな！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.29,0:11:58.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,…白い花
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.42,0:12:03.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そんなに見られると…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.97,0:12:09.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸って、人の魂が見えるんでしょ？魂の色が
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.06,0:12:12.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私のは…あんまり見ないで
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.60,0:12:17.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,きっと…すごく汚れてる  すごく
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:24.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,不思議…この手は嫌じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.54,0:12:31.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殿からの叱責じゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.45,0:12:32.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,では、兵糧は
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:35.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それは送るとある 援軍もな！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:38.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だが…それを待っていては恥じゃ！動くぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.05,0:12:42.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,奇襲を仕掛ける！決して悟られるな！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.22,0:12:46.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,酒井の間者にはよくよく用心するよう、申し伝えよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.55,0:12:47.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.52,0:12:56.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,仕事かい？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.27,0:13:00.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そっか…あんた、私の仕事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.98,0:13:02.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいら、わざと覗いたわけじゃ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.95,0:13:07.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いいの  私は恥ずかしいとは思ってないから
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.95,0:13:09.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,行きていくためだもの
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.41,0:13:14.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でも、あんたが近寄りたくないのもわかる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:16.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,汚れ仕事だものね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:23.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それにしても…あんたくらいの歳で、よく私の仕事がわかったね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.42,0:13:27.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいら、おっかちゃんとずっと旅してて  色々…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.59,0:13:33.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そんとき、どんなに腹が減っても おっかちゃんが絶対やらなかった仕事だから
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.73,0:13:36.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そう　偉いお母ちゃんね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.98,0:13:39.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だけど…そうやって
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.07,0:13:42.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おっかちゃんは死んじまった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.69,0:13:48.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おっかちゃんは偉いけど、生きてる姉ちゃんも同じくらい偉ぇよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.24,0:13:54.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,偉ぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.16,0:13:59.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戦でなくしたモン、戦から取り戻してやるんだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.92,0:14:03.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今度はぶん取ってやれ！田んぼも畑もぜーんぶ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.09,0:14:07.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うん  ありがとね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:28.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき  メシ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:31.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さぁ どんどん食べて精つけなよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:33.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,片足取られたぐらい何だよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.16,0:14:37.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,声取り戻したんだから、黙ってねぇで喋んなよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.91,0:14:41.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ほれほれ、食べなきゃ出る声も出ねぇからな？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.71,0:14:44.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,水水！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.01,0:14:48.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わりぃわりぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.55,0:14:53.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぁ…あにき…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:56.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,鬼神なんかに負けねぇよな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.48,0:15:00.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきが鬼神なんかに、なるわけねぇよな！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:07.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき！そんなことよりどんどん食べてくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.16,0:15:21.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,赤い花つんで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.42,0:15:27.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの人にあげよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.59,0:15:29.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:39.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私は仕事行ってくるけど、百鬼丸を行かせちゃダメよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.14,0:15:42.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まだ戦いなんて無理だから
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.44,0:15:43.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わかってるって
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.73,0:15:49.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,すげぇな！手に仕込んであるのか！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:52.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でも！俺たちだっていいモン持ってるぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.66,0:16:01.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いくさ場で集めたんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:03.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ほら！これなんていいだろう！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.03,0:16:30.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,母ちゃん…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.66,0:16:39.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきー！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:51.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こりゃひと雨来るぞぉ～！助かったぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:56.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ミオ姉！大変だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:16:58.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸が鬼神退治に行っちまった！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:01.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どろろが追いかけてった！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.35,0:17:47.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきー！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.49,0:18:03.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ？なんじゃ！ぬか喜びかい！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.09,0:18:22.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まったく…おいらに黙って行くなんてひでぇよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.31,0:18:24.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,姉ちゃんも心配してるぞ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:27.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まぁ、足が戻ってよかったな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.52,0:18:28.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうしたあにき…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.94,0:18:34.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,寺が！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:42.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,残党がいないか確かめろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.08,0:18:45.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだよ…これ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.08,0:18:47.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どういうことだよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.50,0:18:52.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだお前 こいつらの仲間か！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:19:00.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この女は戦犯 わが陣にいかがわしい商売をしに来たが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:03.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ゆうべ酒井の陣に入るのが目撃された
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.80,0:19:07.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,密偵の疑いありとして早急に処分されたのじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.14,0:19:10.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,姉ちゃん！タケ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.85,0:19:15.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,離せバカヤロ！お前ら、なんで…なんで！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.94,0:19:20.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その取り乱しよう…やはり仲間か！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:34.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだお前！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.88,0:19:36.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こいつの手！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.55,0:19:39.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,姉ちゃんしっかり！タケ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.97,0:19:45.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,赤い花つん…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:48.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,姉ちゃん…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:50.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ…のひ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.19,0:19:58.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,斬れぃ！斬れぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.32,0:20:03.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.87,0:20:07.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,貴様ぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.46,0:20:19.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.64,0:20:37.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,穴ぐらから出てきたモンが 鬼だったってことにならねぇようにしなよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.11,0:20:45.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,た、助けてくれぇ…助けてくれぇ！頼む、助けてぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.66,0:20:51.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やめろあにき！やめてくれ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.83,0:20:55.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ダメだ！鬼になっちゃダメだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.04,0:20:59.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,頼む！頼むよあにき！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.92,0:21:05.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき…姉ちゃんが持ってたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.89,0:21:12.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,種籾だ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.48,0:21:15.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ちゃんと侍から取り戻したんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.60,0:21:17.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,田んぼを作る…ために…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.11,0:21:20.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,姉ちゃんは負けてねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.98,0:21:22.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきも負けないでくれよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.53,0:21:24.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,頼むよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.75,0:21:37.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,み…お…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.56,0:21:55.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ほら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.02,0:22:04.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,赤い花つんで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.32,0:22:10.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの人にあげよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.70,0:22:17.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの人の髪に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.67,0:22:23.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この花さしてあげよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.40,0:22:45.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,憂鬱が風に散らばり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.11,0:22:48.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,吹き溜まって影になる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.15,0:22:55.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,僕らの足音は　無用を饒舌に諭す
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.37,0:23:02.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,君の瞳の深さを覗き見て狼狽える
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.21,0:23:07.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,望みなどあったでしょうか　この行き先には
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.13,0:23:12.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戯けて笑うのは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.39,0:23:15.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この道が暗いから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.72,0:23:22.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,灯りを灯すのに　僕がいるでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.61,0:23:25.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さよならごっこは慣れたもんさ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.90,0:23:28.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でも手を振ったら泣いちゃった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.15,0:23:35.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,僕らの真っ赤な悲しみが 暮れる 暮れる そして夜が来る
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.58,0:23:38.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,当たり前にやってくる明日なら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.83,0:23:41.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,生きたいなんて言わなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.08,0:23:48.76,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よせばいいのに夢見てしまう 未来 未来 君のせいなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.01,0:23:59.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,"Arijigoku"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.34,0:00:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru got injured \Ndue to the sudden return of his hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.77,0:00:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl named Mio took him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.14,0:00:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio lived with children who \Nhad been orphaned in the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.48,0:00:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But on the night Hyakkimaru went out \Nto fight a demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.37,0:00:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't... I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.21,0:00:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.67,0:00:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.80,0:00:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect, help me out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.26,0:00:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.68,0:00:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,His leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.30,0:01:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He shouldn't have fought with that injury. \NThe demon got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.27,0:01:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.40,0:01:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.23,0:01:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he lost his leg \Nbut got his voice back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.57,0:01:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru's voice...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.08,0:01:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Party is over
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.96,0:01:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still wanna dance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.59,0:01:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.13,0:01:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday, one day my passion's fire will
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.89,0:01:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,From the beginning I knew
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.81,0:01:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,One day the flames would die out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.52,0:01:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I thought I didn't need anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.36,0:01:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But even now, I'm so serious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.86,0:02:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I still have time to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.49,0:02:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... but I'm gonna burn it up, baby
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.54,0:02:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry darling, it's not that easy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.50,0:02:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But surely it's not that bad either
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.88,0:02:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me fire
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.84,0:02:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Light it up, baby. \NI'm gonna burn it up, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.57,0:02:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Party is over
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.32,0:02:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry darling Hurry up \NAh... I still have time to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.16,0:02:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry darling Hurry up \NAh... I still have time to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.99,0:02:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me fire
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.87,0:02:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Light it up, baby. \NI'm gonna burn it up, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.12,0:02:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,#6 The story of the Moriko Song, part 2
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.43,0:03:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.84,0:03:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.97,0:03:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.39,0:03:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.56,0:03:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do? You're hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing, I just tripped.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.48,0:03:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay? You need to rest up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.74,0:03:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you that you shouldn't work \Nat both camps.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop going...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.91,0:03:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.33,0:03:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.71,0:03:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.38,0:03:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just too early for him to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio, never mind him. Get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.81,0:03:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, I'm used to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You get food ready for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What, shouldn't you be \Nkeeping watch over your guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.26,0:04:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.30,0:04:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But Mio will take good care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.18,0:04:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, Mio sure likes \Nto take care of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,After working all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Take, have you ever seen \Nyour sis at work?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.40,0:04:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I always stay home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.45,0:04:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't leave the little ones alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.78,0:04:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.99,0:04:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, we have to rely on her \Nor we'll all starve to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not blaming you or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We all made a promise together \Nto someday own our own rice paddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.92,0:05:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Rice paddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.17,0:05:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna be all green in the summer \Nand golden in the fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.51,0:05:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Golden, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.89,0:05:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll grow more rice than we can eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.52,0:05:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We've only seen rice paddies burnt by war \Nor dried up by droughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.52,0:05:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But Mio said \Nthey all used to be golden.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make our very own rice paddy \Nsome day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.11,0:05:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Green and golden. And all ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.79,0:05:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be able to work too in a little bit, \Nso Mio won't have to work so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.33,0:05:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Take.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.22,0:05:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.47,0:05:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,War took a lot from us, \Nso let's get it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:05:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We need a good rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.27,0:06:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. \NWe're blessed by rains every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.32,0:06:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,See? There are clouds coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.41,0:06:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me join the army \Nto suppress the Sakai clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll crush that little domain \Nlike it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.84,0:06:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Never underestimate wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's how you think, it's too early \Nfor you. Back to your training.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-Father! \N-Tahomaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, please tell Father \Nto let me go to war.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father just said no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.31,0:06:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Then no it is, no matter what I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Father doesn't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.32,0:06:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If only he'd let me go,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.57,0:06:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I'd distinguish myself in battle \Nand make you proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.37,0:06:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Of all things...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My feats wouldn't impress you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:07:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you are always like that, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what prize I hunt down or \Nhow great I am at martial arts,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.55,0:07:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you never care.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.72,0:07:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not like things to do with war.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not war you do not like, \Nbut me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Tahomaru, what mother \Nwould not love her child?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.24,0:07:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyogo, Mutsu. I wish to go riding. \NBring the horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to say it. \NI was being a bit childish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.26,0:07:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Her lady is kind. \NEspecially to you, always.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.60,0:08:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother has never been unkind to me. \NYet...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.31,0:08:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master, please, that is dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You shall get hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.49,0:08:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyogo, Mutsu, help him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.53,0:08:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-Please, Young Master! \N-Do come down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.66,0:08:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.12,0:08:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, you mustn't be up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There is something else that \NMother cares for much more in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She will never say it, \Nbut she is hiding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.18,0:08:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just Mother. \NIt's the same for Father, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.01,0:08:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You, I, this domain. \NWe all sit atop a small cornerstone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.15,0:08:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do not forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.07,0:08:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What can they be hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.06,0:09:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You must stay put.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.44,0:09:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't go. I understand that \Nyou're frustrated, but what if you die?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.36,0:09:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I pushed myself too hard as well, \Nso I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.20,0:09:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it wasn't easy to make money.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.87,0:09:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd already promised I'd never cry \Nbecause of a samurai ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.17,0:09:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You too. \NIf you try too hard and die, you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:10:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, I heard you found your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.26,0:10:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing. Try to say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your voice too loud for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.11,0:10:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.82,0:10:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Dororo said you were like \Na beast in a cave the way you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How about a song? You like songs, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.08,0:10:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick a red flower
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.71,0:10:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I sing whenever I feel sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.09,0:10:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick a red flower
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.93,0:10:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,To give to her
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,In her hair
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.11,0:11:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I will put the flower
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.20,0:11:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.66,0:11:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, just like that girl says, \NI'll take it slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.37,0:11:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just go around the place \Nthe monster is. I'm in no hurry anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.09,0:11:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Although it'd be useless \Nto try and tell Hyakkimaru that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.42,0:11:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If you take a toy from a baby, \Nit'll get mad and take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.76,0:11:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Same as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.56,0:11:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially since what they took \Nfrom him is his own body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He's calm when he's listening \Nto that song.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.81,0:11:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The demon flames Hyakkimaru has had \Nsince he was a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You could say they're the embers \Nleft from when they took his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You better hope the beast that comes out \Nof the cave isn't a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.92,0:11:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.29,0:11:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...white flower
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.42,0:12:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.97,0:12:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see people's souls, right? \NThe colors of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.06,0:12:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't look at mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.60,0:12:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably filthy. Really filthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How strange. I don't loathe these hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.54,0:12:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Daigo is angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.45,0:12:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So no provisions?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll send them. Reinforcements, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But it would be an embarrassment to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.05,0:12:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We will plan a surprise attack. \NDon't let them sense it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.22,0:12:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell everyone to be on the watch \Nfor Sakai spies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.55,0:12:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.52,0:12:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Going to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.27,0:13:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you know what my job is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.98,0:13:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't look on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.95,0:13:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, I'm not ashamed about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.95,0:13:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.41,0:13:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But I understand \Nif you want to keep your distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a nice job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm amazed at how a boy your age \Nunderstood what my job was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.42,0:13:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I traveled around with my mama a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.59,0:13:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's the only job Mama didn't do \Nno matter how hungry we got.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.73,0:13:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What an admirable mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.98,0:13:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.07,0:13:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how she died...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.69,0:13:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama was admirable, \Nbut so are you for staying alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.24,0:13:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You are, darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.16,0:13:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna take back \Nwhat war took from you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.92,0:14:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Then take it all! \NRice paddies, farms, everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.09,0:14:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I will. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, it'll make you stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So what if you lost a leg?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.16,0:14:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You got your voice back, \Nso say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.91,0:14:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you need to eat \Nif you want to use that voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.71,0:14:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, have some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.01,0:14:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.55,0:14:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hyakkimaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't lose to it, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.48,0:15:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never become a monster, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, eat up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.16,0:15:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick a red flower
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.42,0:15:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,To give to her
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.59,0:15:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In her...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.01,0:15:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to work, \Nbut don't let Hyakkimaru go to fight it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.14,0:15:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,His body isn't ready for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.44,0:15:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.73,0:15:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so cool. It's stuck on your arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But we've got something cool, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.66,0:16:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We found them at the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, pretty nice, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.03,0:16:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.66,0:16:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like the rain's coming. Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio, we're in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:16:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru went to beat the monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Dororo went after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.35,0:17:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.49,0:18:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it? Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.09,0:18:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, how could you go without telling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.31,0:18:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio is worried, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But good thing your leg grew back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.52,0:18:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.94,0:18:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The temple...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Check for any more survivors.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.08,0:18:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.08,0:18:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.50,0:18:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you? Are you one of them too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:19:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This girl came to do lewd business \Nat our camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But we saw her enter the Sakai camp \Nlast night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.80,0:19:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been disposed of \Nfor being a suspected spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.14,0:19:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio, Take!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.85,0:19:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go, idiot! How could you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.94,0:19:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you're one of them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.88,0:19:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,His arms...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.55,0:19:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio, wake up! Take!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.97,0:19:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick a red flower
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,To give to her
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.19,0:19:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.32,0:20:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.87,0:20:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You devil...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.46,0:20:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Hyakkimaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.64,0:20:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You better hope the beast that comes out \Nof the cave isn't a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.11,0:20:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Spare me, please, I beg you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.66,0:20:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Hyakkimaru, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.83,0:20:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't! You can't turn into a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.04,0:20:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Please bro, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.92,0:21:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru, Mio had this with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.89,0:21:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's seed rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.48,0:21:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,She really got it back from the samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.60,0:21:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,To make her own rice paddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.11,0:21:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.98,0:21:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can't lose either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.53,0:21:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.75,0:21:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi... o...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.56,0:21:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.02,0:22:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick a red flower
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.32,0:22:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,To give to her
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.70,0:22:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In her hair
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.67,0:22:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I will put the flower
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.40,0:22:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorrow scatters in the wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.11,0:22:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,piling up to form shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.15,0:22:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Our footsteps admonish \Nindifference in such verbose ways
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.37,0:23:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As I peek into your fathomless eyes, \NI lose my composure
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.21,0:23:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any hope \Nin the place I am heading to?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.13,0:23:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I feign amusement and laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.39,0:23:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,because this road is so dark
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.72,0:23:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be there to shine the light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.61,0:23:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm used to playing at saying goodbye,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.90,0:23:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but I cried when I waved to you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.15,0:23:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Our fiery woes fade... and fade... \Nuntil night falls upon us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.58,0:23:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If I knew tomorrow would be so mundane,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.83,0:23:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have said that I wanted to live
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.08,0:23:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's futile but can't help dreaming \Nof a future... a future... you are to blame
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.01,0:23:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"Arijigoku"
